I wouldn't know. He moved to Temecula.

76
00:03:54.359 --> 00:03:56.611
Oh. I'm... I'm sorry.

77
00:03:56.694 --> 00:03:58.821
- I didn't...
- No. I'm much happier now.

78
00:03:58.905 --> 00:04:01.366
You... you seem... changed.

79
00:04:01.449 --> 00:04:04.577
- Can I go now?
