83
00:04:13.503 --> 00:04:17.632
Uppers. downers. hydrocodone. lorazepam.

84
00:04:17.714 --> 00:04:18.675
Lorazepam?

85
00:04:18.966 --> 00:04:20.802
Yeah. It's good.

86
00:04:20.885 --> 00:04:22.053
Okay.

87
00:04:23.304 --> 00:04:24.597
All right. Well. um...

88
