122
00:06:39.774 --> 00:06:41.734
On leave. Santa Ana PD.

123
00:06:41.943 --> 00:06:45.446
Hey. maybe you know Pete Austin.

124
00:06:45.863 --> 00:06:47.865
transferred down here in 2012.

125
00:06:48.074 --> 00:06:49.951
mustache. kind of...

126
00:06:50.576 --> 00:06:52.036
kind of cold sense of humor?

127
00:06:53.413 --> 00:06:54.288
No.

128
00:06:55.540 --> 00:06:59.293
Okay. Well. I offered to help
Mrs. Harding out and.

129
