you know. maybe liaise with you.
help relay any information.

130
00:07:03.881 --> 00:07:05.716
You know this case
has been open for months.

131
00:07:05.967 --> 00:07:07.385
More help is not what we need.

132
00:07:07.468 --> 00:07:10.096
- You need a lead.
- I do. And I don't have one.

133
00:07:10.304 --> 00:07:11.305
Wow. not one?

134
