and act like an asshole.

152
00:08:02.648 --> 00:08:03.733
Okay. You're one to talk.

153
00:08:03.816 --> 00:08:06.360
Okay. You know what? Hey!
I'm not fucking around right now.

154
00:08:06.611 --> 00:08:09.238
No laptop. no phone. no TV.

155
00:08:09.822 --> 00:08:13.117
That is just the start. Because I can't
think of anything more creative right now.

156
00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:15.536
- Whatever.
- No. not whatever. Stop. Hey!

157
00:08:16.829 --> 00:08:18.456
The dominoes have fallen. bro.

158
00:08:18.789 --> 00:08:19.749
You pushed them.

159
00:08:19.999 --> 00:08:22.502
And you pushed me.
which was a really bad idea.

160
00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:26.422
I'm not scared of you.

161
00:08:27.507 --> 00:08:29.133
Well. you should be scared of me.

162
00:08:35.139 --> 00:08:38.017
Ooh! Is that beer?
I would love one if there's more.

163
00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:39.769
Actually. this is Charlie's pee.

164
00:08:40.144 --> 00:08:42.188
There's no more.
but I'm sure he could make you some.

165
00:08:44.065 --> 00:08:44.982
Is he on drugs?

166
00:08:45.733 --> 00:08:48.903
I don't know.
but he is definitely selling pills.

167
00:08:49.028 --> 00:08:50.613
- No.
- Uh-huh. Yup.

168
00:08:51.072 --> 00:08:53.366
Ted was the good parent
