170
00:08:57.119 --> 00:08:58.079
It's bad.

171
00:08:58.538 --> 00:09:00.206
I've just...
I've been asleep at the wheel.

172
00:09:00.373 --> 00:09:02.166
How are you supposed to know
what's he's doing?

173
00:09:02.333 --> 00:09:03.501
They're not your pills. right?

174
00:09:04.418 --> 00:09:05.628
No. Oh...

175
00:09:07.547 --> 00:09:09.423
- Look at you!
- Too formal?

176
00:09:10.007 --> 00:09:11.926
Uh... For a class recital. maybe.

177
00:09:12.301 --> 00:09:14.136
That's okay. I've got a strong second.

178
00:09:14.262 --> 00:09:15.263
Okay.

179
00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.056
Oh.

180
00:09:18.307 --> 00:09:19.559
What's the verdict?

181
00:09:20.601 --> 00:09:21.602
It's all clean.

182
00:09:21.769 --> 00:09:23.104
Oh. I mean. fuck!

183
00:09:23.187 --> 00:09:24.814
Fucking... He could've killed a kid.

184
00:09:25.022 --> 00:09:26.983
Imagine if he murdered someone.

185
00:09:27.233 --> 00:09:29.110
