- Yeah. but...

186
00:09:29.193 --> 00:09:30.820
It would definitely ruin his life.

187
00:09:31.279 --> 00:09:33.573
And him carrying
around the burden of that?

188
00:09:33.864 --> 00:09:34.949
Ooh. that'd be heavy.

189
00:09:35.032 --> 00:09:36.826
