- Is this handsome?

197
00:09:53.259 --> 00:09:55.595
- So handsome.
<i>- </i>The handsomest.

198
00:09:57.471 --> 00:09:58.931
At least there's him.

199
00:09:59.015 --> 00:10:00.641
- He's perfect.
- He is.

200
00:10:03.978 --> 00:10:07.732
<i>♪ I believe the children</i>
<i>Are our future ♪</i>

201
00:10:08.065 --> 00:10:12.194
<i>♪ Teach them well
And let them lead the way ♪</i>

202
00:10:12.403 --> 00:10:18.326
<i>♪ Show them all the beauty
They possess inside ♪</i>

203
00:10:18.534 --> 00:10:21.162
He is by far the best one.
which is not saying a ton.

204
00:10:21.245 --> 00:10:24.040
I know. Thanks.
Definitely got his dad's musical genes.

205
00:10:24.540 --> 00:10:26.292
He should be in the kid's choir
at my church.

206
00:10:26.375 --> 00:10:28.252
Sure. When I die.

207
00:10:28.669 --> 00:10:32.340
<i>♪ Everybody searching for a hero</i> ♪

208
00:10:32.923 --> 00:10:35.551
