210
00:10:37.803 --> 00:10:40.890
Oh. she's in the front row.
to the left. there.

211
00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:44.644
I feel so bad for her.

212
00:10:46.228 --> 00:10:48.606
I know. Her mother named her Shandy.

213
00:10:48.731 --> 00:10:50.441
Mmm. And put her in that dress.

214
00:10:51.651 --> 00:10:55.154
- Sad.
- ♪ <i>I decided long ago ♪</i>

215
00:10:56.113 --> 00:11:00.534
<i>♪ Never to walk in anyone's shadow</i> ♪

216
00:11:00.868 --> 00:11:04.205
