238
00:12:10.479 --> 00:12:11.981
I got hit by a bus.

239
00:12:12.064 --> 00:12:14.817
Oh. my God. And that's your only injury?

240
00:12:14.900 --> 00:12:15.860
Yeah.

241
00:12:16.235 --> 00:12:20.531
Well. I ruptured my spleen.
and splintered my coccyx. and...

242
00:12:21.198 --> 00:12:23.701
- perforated my eardrum.
- Oh.

243
00:12:28.122 --> 00:12:29.248
Hi. Shandy.

244
00:12:29.874 --> 00:12:30.833
Hi!

